## GOAL

Train a **2D slice-based unconditional diffusion model** (DDIM) for brain MRI synthesis.
Input data: skull-stripped, multi-modal brain MRI NIfTI files.
Current scope: T1-only, 3D volumetric subjects only, unconditional generation.

